Kylie Minogue releases Boombox, a collection of remixes on January 5th 2009! The album features some of Kylie's most popular tracks, and some lesser known gems remixed to perfection by some of the best dance producers around including Chemical Brothers, Fischerspooner, Mylo and Sebastien Leger.
